snippet.title: PAC-MAN 256 - PS4/XB1/PC - 4X Multi PAC-MAN (Announcement Trailer)
snippet.description:
PAC-MAN 256 is coming to consoles and PC!
A brand new version of the highly acclaimed PAC-MAN 256 game has been announced for a digital release on June 21st on PlayStation 4, Xbox One and PC through Steam.
This new version will let you play with up to 4 friends via the local co-op multiplayer mode. 

Like us: https://www.facebook.com/pacman
Follow us: https://twitter.com/Bandainamcoeu
Visit us: https://www.pac-man256.com
